              </div>
              <div
                class="relative z-10 w-20 h-20 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6 shadow-inner group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
              >
                👥
              </div>
              <h3
